  <official_title>Open-Label, 40-weeks Extension of Protocol MCS-2-TWN-a to Further Evaluate the Efficacy and Safety of MCS-2 for the Treatment of Lower Urinary Tract Symptoms Suggestive of Benign Prostatic Hyperplasia in Treatment Na√Øve Male Subjects</official_title>
